To enable the numbered page navigation style, open your `pages.php` file then search for a line of code that look like this or this:

~~~ .html
<nav><?php echo $pager; ?></nav>
~~~

~~~ .php
<?php Shield::get('pager'); ?>
~~~

Replace with this:

~~~ .php
<?php Shield::get('pager/step'); ?>
~~~